<br>
Are you MAD?!?!?!  Our Epic Rules!  An 800 point self-rune that not only adds mana regen, but doesnt use any DOTS?  What more do ya need?<br>
<br>
Our epic is amazing!  In crowd control situations (in groups with no chanter) where multi's are pulled, I nuke/aggro the add, lead it away, and root it.  Usually, it doesnt get through my rune before it's parked.<br>
<br>
Additionally, when the healers are LOM, I nuke early to get aggro off the tanks (saves the healer from having to heal the tanks).  After the rune drops, I stun/root the mob, back up, re-rune, and then wade back in to either tank or nuke.  NOTE: Over-nuking in these situations can actually be a good thing if done right... esp. when up close and person... so as to not ping-pong the mob.<br>
